metadata.name: his eyes still stayed
metadata.description:
the youth had left. Turning back for a long time, the middle-aged man relaxed his grip on the hilt of his sword when he was deep inside the Praetorian Guard. There was a cold look in his eyes and he said with indifference, "Take these thieves to the trial of the Tingwei Government, and find out their identity..."



"Kill THREE CLANS!!"
